snippet.title: Body of Evidence Switch and Xbox One Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
►WWW http://boethegame.com
►STEAM https://store.steampowered.com/app/656830/Body_of_Evidence
►FACEBOOK https://www.facebook.com/BoEtheGame
►TWITTER https://twitter.com/evidencebody
►INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/bodyofevidencegame

Become a dead body disposal specialist. You need to hide the body and clean the mess before someone arrives. Remember, you’re on a clock. Use proper tools and be thorough because one smear of blood will get you in trouble.
